atmss.bams

Class BAMSHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • atmss.bams.BAMSHandler
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BAMSCommunicator

    public class BAMSHandler
extends Object
    The BAMSHandler class is an interface between ATMSS and BAMS. It is used to invoke different PHP programs resided on web server for various functions related to BAMS.
